      <Statement>Solve unit rate problems including those involving unit pricing and constant speed. &lt;i&gt;For example, if it took 7 hours to mow 4 lawns, then at that rate, how many lawns could be mowed in 35 hours? At what rate were lawns being mowed?&lt;/i&gt;</Statement>
